  "3102340": {
    "name": "Princess of the Water Lilies",
    "steam_appid": 3102340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/35524b150a1aad50f287cc3d96f80ca8.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=240 /></span>《公主猫物语》是一款2D平台游戏，玩家将化身为一只猫咪，探索大自然与人造物的世界。她从小被一个青蛙家庭收养，在宁静的池塘边长大，并获赠一条神奇的项圈，开启了她独特的力量，呼噜魔法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当她发出呼噜声时，项圈便会释放魔法能量，改变周遭的环境; 使花朵绽放、桥梁生长，让奄奄一息的生命重获新生。以呼噜魔法解救她的家人与家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/33b5b5ab62364e5ea5c5039924eac01a.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=103 /></span>借助小猫的魔法项圈改变环境，解开从简单互动到多阶段复杂的谜题。探索这奇妙的手绘生态区域，跨越障碍，寻找隐秘道路，揭开世界的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/4fb3bc74c23702e46296d2188e3decaf.poster.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/4fb3bc74c23702e46296d2188e3decaf.webm?t=1770212225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/1d0b9e6d2edf5491b3ed52d965f06732.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=103 /></span>随着冒险的进行，呼噜魔法不仅能帮助你解谜， 也能提升跳跃和探索体验，比如藤蔓摆荡、水面穿行等多样玩法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/cd6a6e822e4ac662ea38016e83d55629.poster.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/cd6a6e822e4ac662ea38016e83d55629.webm?t=1770212225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/85343a23fda4955ecf07ccc905565f59.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=103 /></span>用最少的文字，通过生动的动画和视觉元素传达故事，让每位玩家都能沉浸式体验故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/36f65b9e84536b79708998adcb25759f.poster.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/36f65b9e84536b79708998adcb25759f.webm?t=1770212225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/5ffe5005e5a829be792b2eefa6c8a224.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=103 /></span>每个章节的终点，等待你的将是精彩的 Boss 战。你必须熟练技能和运用呼噜魔法，才能在这场多样化的强敌，成为最终胜者。<br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/e30e5e8f506cbca114daf1504b805e97.poster.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/e30e5e8f506cbca114daf1504b805e97.webm?t=1770212225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/334a3342aa64d56a3211849ea6b554db.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=103 /></span>每一帧都由鲜活的手绘动画呈现，配合沉浸式管弦乐，让玩家体验既怀旧又充满新意的精彩世界。<br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/c0ad9118322770a5a7c731467c51bc5e.poster.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/c0ad9118322770a5a7c731467c51bc5e.webm?t=1770212225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/cd61f6cb3f54fba58b415d1faa07d1b8.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1200 height=103 /></span>致敬动画黄金时代的的画风，讲述温暖而奇幻的故事，充满魔法生物与冒险元素。<br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/43078c8ad4115fbf4a8132448f524049.poster.avif?t=1770212225\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102340/extras/43078c8ad4115fbf4a8132448f524049.webm?t=1770212225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是在解开复杂谜题，还是探索如画的世界，《公主猫物语》适合所有年龄层的玩家，并带你踏上令人心动的魔法旅程。</p>",
